		<div style="text-align:right;width:100%;padding-bottom:20px">
			<a href="/process/signin" style="color:green">Sign in</a> | 
			<a href="/process/signup" style="color:green">Sign up</a> |
			<a href="/process/intro" style="color:green">About TiK</a>
		</div>
		<div class="ui container" style="padding-bottom:20px">
			<div class="ui basic center aligned segment">
				<div class="ui blue segment" style="margin-bottom:30px;padding:10px">
					<div style="font-size:15px;font-height:20px"><img src="../../images/double_quote1.png" style="width:25px;height:30px"> <strong>We will purchase your review.</strong> <img src="../../images/double_quote2.png" style="width:25px;height:30px"></div> 
					<div style="font-size:15px;text-align:right;padding-top:10px">- Harris Lim</div></div>
				<div style="padding:10px">Hi guys. We are TIK(Travel In Korea).<br>We want to make a travel plans for foreigners who want to travel in Korea without the cost. Nowadays there are too many travel companies all over the world.<br>The travel plans are uploaded on their website and travelers have to choose one type of their plans.<br>Plans which is uploaded in website is not focus on travelers. That is just companies idea.<br>But TIK is different. We consider travelers travel style! We ask your travel style at Ask page(you can see after signin) and try to make a good travel plans for you. We want to help your free traveling in Korea and can <strong>be your travel helpers.</strong><br><br>You can see the under images how to use TIK!<br>Thank you.</div>
				<div class="ui mini steps" style="padding-bottom:20px">
